import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { ActivatedRoute } from '@angular/router'; import { IUserExtension } from '../user-extension.model'; @Component({ selector: 'jhi-user-extension-detail', templateUrl: './user-extension-detail.component.html', }) export class UserExtensionDetailComponent implements OnInit { userExtension: IUserExtension | null = null; constructor(protected activatedRoute: ActivatedRoute) {} ngOnInit(): void { this.activatedRoute.data.subscribe(({ userExtension }) => { this.userExtension = userExtension; }); } previousState(): void { window.history.back(); } }
